{"tid":610559,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"fanpiece: 很多連登仔留言都沒有水準","createTime":"2018-03-30T05:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T07:41:00.000Z","uid":66260,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"68377e52d4e73c1e6fc06b5ccdb8fb49110d26a9","tid":610559,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ent.fanpiece.com/purestalker/張敬軒掩飾身份與連登仔對話-出乎意料結果反映連登質素-c1315857.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.fanpiece.com%2Fpurestalker%2F%E5%BC%B5%E6%95%AC%E8%BB%92%E6%8E%A9%E9%A3%BE%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%88%87%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-%E5%87%BA%E4%B9%8E%E6%84%8F%E6%96%99%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%A0-c1315857.html&d=DE904%2F16tISvZ0qSGm9fkDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=dec100d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.fanpiece.com/purestalker/張敬軒掩飾身份與連登仔對話-出乎意料結果反映連登質素-c1315857.html</a><br />\n<br />\n連登討論區是年輕人講時事、娛樂、八卦的集中地，不過很多連登仔留言都沒有水準，以匿名方式批評、針對現實中看不順眼的同學、藝人、朋友，甚至說出侮辱性的說話。<br />\n<br />\n(中刪)<br />\n<br />\n其實連登雖然使用量已經超越高登，不過高登始終比較高質，以前部份潮文更被拍成真實電影。現在連登以好評、負評、回覆量來決定熱門帖文，很多人以投票、標題黨等方式騙取會員注意，令整體討論區質素每下愈況。連登經常被用家投訴小朋友過多，出現很多沒質素的會員。"},{"pid":"dc2176124a108f9d8fc2bfdf0e00e54a3ca74c32","tid":610559,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb521fc5e678c3faf170a73c23464cdaa8294ee","tid":610559,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:24:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d420aeaf8d34381541a15cb6f5df7b4bc7c99c82","tid":610559,"uid":4525,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:31:44.000Z","msg":"fanpiece真係每況愈下<br />\n講到高登冇標題黨/呃正負評<br />\n咁又係，人都無，點呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\"